                     <title type="Incomplete" ref="LIT1019Actsof">Acts of the Apostles</title>
                     <note>
                        The arrangement of the text is incorrect and some parts are missing. The sequence according to the original arrangement is: 
                        1, 9 (<q xml:lang="gez">ወእንዘ፡</q>, on <locus target="#15r"/>) - 2, 3 (<q xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡</q>, on <locus target="#16v"/>); 
