                        4, 30 (<q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡</q>, on <locus target="#1r"/>) - 7, 32  (<q xml:lang="gez">ወአምላ<supplied reason="lost">ከ፡</supplied></q>, on <locus target="#8v"/>); 
                        18, 27 (<q xml:lang="gez">ጸሐፋ፡</q>, on <locus target="#17r"/>) - 26,5 (<q xml:lang="gez">አበ<supplied reason="lost">ዊነ፡</supplied></q>, on <locus target="#34v"/>). 
                        Numerous corrections and additions were inserted by <persName ref="PRS9286Tasfase">Tasfā Ṣǝyon</persName>, 
                        as well as of numbers indicating the pages of <bibl><ptr target="bm:Petrus1548Test"/><citedRange unit="fol">133-157</citedRange></bibl>. 
                     </note>
